  "contentHtml": "<h2>How to redraw a city, Out Loud</h2>\n<p><span>You can listen to </span><em>How to redraw a city</em><span> here or on </span><a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/gb/podcast/how-to-redraw-a-city-by-anya-martin/id1819488714?i=1000755014847\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Apple</a><span>, </span><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/episode/5DQeHkAkNBJMKK3461FF2H?si=328982f3bc4d4ba9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Spotify</a><span>, </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FCAX-2qYYCk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">YouTube</a><span>, or wherever you find your podcasts.</span><br><br><span>You can see the images, graphs and read the article on our </span><a href=\"https://worksinprogress.co/issue/how-to-redraw-a-city/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">website</a><span>.</span><br><br><span>Words by </span><strong>Anya Martin</strong><br><span>Read by </span><strong>Stuart Ritchie</strong><br><span>Music by </span><strong>David Hackett</strong></p>\n<h4>Discussion about this video</h4>\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!vCd1!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fvideo_upload%2Fpost%2F191248220%2Fc0d2b390-4632-466d-b78f-43f1fb07b498%2Ftranscoded-1773752748.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!WcfC!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fvideo_upload%2Fpost%2F191242596%2F4a5dcbeb-49fb-492c-950b-45d993aa51d7%2Ftranscoded-1773751205.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!2p1p!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fvideo_upload%2Fpost%2F191239405%2F85056331-fbbc-47c7-b235-